            "body": "> before [9f90992](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/9f909929344287bc1246d6b4dab55d500b514396) the windows ti defs would just get cleared.\r\n\r\nI can't reproduce that (neither with my revert nor with `git checkout 9f90992934^`).\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/36736 says the problem was reproducible with `tic -V = ncurses 6.0.20150808` on MacOS, and I can't help but wonder if we can really expect a 10+ years old version of ncurses to be able to work with current terminfo.src…",
